{"tid":1625673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【公屋冇地位？】藍田公屋豪裝靚過私樓　網民超葡萄：首先要有間公屋囉！","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T09:37:31.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e261211529296f86cb758f00b10f29d6bf04a01","tid":1625673,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789886/org/63bcca80132bcdbe24eff7c7bc80e340.jpg/W4sXVBvwxbhwqHbaybeKLo6A_FiXMEDjA00uDQNNLg0?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789886%2Forg%2F63bcca80132bcdbe24eff7c7bc80e340.jpg%2FW4sXVBvwxbhwqHbaybeKLo6A_FiXMEDjA00uDQNNLg0%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=0cad11fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港樓價持續高企，想上車難過登天，難怪不少人認為有公屋才是人生勝利組，而且因租金便宜，住戶更願意花費在裝修上。近日有網民在facebook群組「裝修佬」發文，分享幾張藍田公屋新裝修的照片，並表示全屋均意大利材料，埋單30萬港元全包，引起大批網民熱議，大讚裝修豪華，「仲靚過豆腐潤私樓」，不過亦有網民相當「葡萄」，笑言不是每人都有機會，「首先，你要有間公屋」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789444/org/36bca7c9798e744eaa4637bd5a942c34.jpg/Bi35p-2GYbaeio10gdbrvxlEYutueFf7TXSNaE10jWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789444%2Forg%2F36bca7c9798e744eaa4637bd5a942c34.jpg%2FBi35p-2GYbaeio10gdbrvxlEYutueFf7TXSNaE10jWg&h=f0929d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名男網民日前在群組上載多張藍田公屋的新裝修照片，從相中所見，公屋以黑白灰顏色為主調，採用大量「盒仔燈」、射燈及假天花，燈光柔和，格局時尚有格調，主人房採用透明玻璃門設計，加上客廳有窗採自然光及開放式廚房，令狹小空間變得開揚寬敞，環境非常舒適。<br />\n<br />\n樓主表示，今次全屋裝修採用意大利材料，總共花費30萬左右，他又大讚裝修師傅手工「頂呱呱」，他自己則最喜歡睡房設計，但未有透露公屋名稱及單位面積。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789446/org/5c5b14958e18614ab1e756f9007bb8c6.jpg/DOrXC5VMUjaBo7Xf_fSXdUFHAKS6AJYT8nmdXfJ5nV0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789446%2Forg%2F5c5b14958e18614ab1e756f9007bb8c6.jpg%2FDOrXC5VMUjaBo7Xf_fSXdUFHAKS6AJYT8nmdXfJ5nV0&h=74fc10d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789448/org/21d07f8187961db9ce0e4bfffe04edfb.jpg/n6-GfYFSOfPqamVoKVggfDmfPMc42zh80xSJEdMUiRE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789448%2Forg%2F21d07f8187961db9ce0e4bfffe04edfb.jpg%2Fn6-GfYFSOfPqamVoKVggfDmfPMc42zh80xSJEdMUiRE&h=c5582527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789450/org/2ad759bce857362393a239e883a5e97e.jpg/apFrGpQXjpCVEfrgKhh03oIMqFYZAqMoQ5FuzkORbs4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789450%2Forg%2F2ad759bce857362393a239e883a5e97e.jpg%2FapFrGpQXjpCVEfrgKhh03oIMqFYZAqMoQ5FuzkORbs4&h=f2557da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789449/org/991ba76d4420b2275a22140f6bd709be.jpg/0FWkS7z9Vc63nH3tIZR_mCYFmNkv10sZU02pAVNNqQE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789449%2Forg%2F991ba76d4420b2275a22140f6bd709be.jpg%2F0FWkS7z9Vc63nH3tIZR_mCYFmNkv10sZU02pAVNNqQE&h=2ee78103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2789451/org/74b02fdd3af945b55858144400a5b525.jpg/S51nXxKvelw_qCpBg8R-Kh4YbVj-NTkdTxlJdk8ZSXY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2789451%2Forg%2F74b02fdd3af945b55858144400a5b525.jpg%2FS51nXxKvelw_qCpBg8R-Kh4YbVj-NTkdTxlJdk8ZSXY&h=86cabcc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6681c897d3b7427a46c4b70af383454e99e3e729","tid":1625673,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:54:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 真係幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個景仲要咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d24cc9535189e8b406dcc43edc5e24bbc599043c","tid":1625673,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"窗係一個敗筆 加個簾會有格調啲"},{"pid":"d88a7bbdd9c34f9b2fd5b0a04e2e627d36b135b5","tid":1625673,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"希望佢入息同資產超標，到時裝修得幾靚都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f22a22de6a679d87ef81283f9b13d32e5980bb","tid":1625673,"uid":295266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"係咪買咗架"},{"pid":"13fb85299c2cd59744a31afb7d877caad9809005","tid":1625673,"uid":326580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"興田？"}]}